OL,3,CFormer sub-postmaster 'honoured' to
OL,4,Cget degree from Bangor University
OL,6,FA former sub-postmaster has been
OL,7,Fpresented with an honorary degree from
OL,8,FBangor University for his contribution
OL,9,Fto public service.
OL,11,FNoel Thomas, 77, from Anglesey, gained
OL,12,Frecognition for his significant role
OL,13,Fin addressing the widespread
OL,14,Fmiscarriage of justice known as the
OL,15,FHorizon scandal in the UK.
