OL,3,CFormer sub-postmaster 'honoured' to
OL,4,Cget degree from Bangor University
OL,6,FEngaging in a prolonged legal battle,
OL,7,Fhe campaigned alongside others to
OL,8,Fclear the names of Post Office
OL,9,Fmanagers who faced criminal
OL,10,Fconvictions due to faulty accounting
OL,11,Fsoftware.
OL,13,FA spokesperson for the university said
OL,14,Fin a statement: "His commitment to
OL,15,Fseeking justice for those affected by
OL,16,Fthe scandal exemplifies his resilience
OL,17,Fand determination to expose the truth."
OL,19,FMr Thomas said receiving the award at
OL,20,Fthe University's Graduation ceremony
OL,21,Fon Tuesday was a "great honour".
