OL,6,F"I thank my family and the press for
OL,7,Fworking on my behalf for the last 18
OL,8,Fyears", he said.
OL,10,F"It's been a great honour to stand
OL,11,Fhere today amongst all these wonderful
OL,12,Fstudents."
OL,14,FProfessor Edmund Burke, Vice-
OL,15,FChancellor, Bangor University said:
OL,16,F"Graduation ceremonies are an
OL,17,Fopportunity to come together to
OL,18,Fcelebrate the success of each and
OL,19,Fevery Bangor student.
