OL,6,F"As well as celebrating each student's
OL,7,Fjourney to being awarded their degree,
OL,8,Fawarding Honorary Degrees allows us to
OL,9,Fshow our appreciation for the impact
OL,10,Fmade by individuals across public
OL,11,Fservice, in the world of literature
OL,12,Fand music, in business, sport or
OL,13,Fscience.
OL,15,F"Our students' stories, and the
